OL,3,CSandro Tonali 'happy' to have helped
OL,4,Cothers with gambling issues during ban
OL,6,FNewcastle United midfielder Sandro
OL,7,FTonali says he hopes his ten-month ban
OL,8,Ffor betting breaches has helped give
OL,9,Fother problem gamblers the strength to
OL,10,Faddress their issues.
OL,12,FThe 24-year-old Italian international
OL,13,Fmoved to St James' Park from AC Milan
OL,14,Fin July 2023 in a #55 million deal,
OL,15,Fonly to be given a worldwide
OL,16,Fsuspension by the Italian Football
OL,17,FFederation in October after admitting
OL,18,Fto a number of gambling offences.
