OL,3,CSandro Tonali 'happy' to have helped
OL,4,Cothers with gambling issues during ban
OL,6,FTonali will be in the squad for the
OL,7,FMagpies' Carabao Cup second round
OL,8,Fclash with Nottingham Forest as the
OL,9,Fban comes to an end.
OL,11,FSpeaking to NUFC TV, he said:
OL,12,F"Especially in the first three months,
OL,13,FI met a lot of people with ordinary
OL,14,Fjobs, especially in Newcastle, who had
OL,15,Fthis problem and who had never spoken
OL,16,Fbefore now.
