OL,3,CSandro Tonali 'happy' to have helped
OL,4,Cothers with gambling issues during ban
OL,6,F"And they did so when it all came out,
OL,7,Fwhen the articles came out and my
OL,8,Fproblem was made public, so after this
OL,9,Fthey decided to get help and stop
OL,10,Fbottling things up, so this made me
OL,11,Fvery happy.
OL,13,F"These people got help just by
OL,14,Ftalking, at first by talking but then
OL,15,Fwith another one thousand ways. But
OL,16,Fthe first step, the biggest step is
OL,17,Fbeing able to talk about this huge
OL,18,Fthing you're carrying inside of you
OL,19,Fthat you've never done before and you
OL,20,Fdon't have the courage to do.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
