OL,3,CSandro Tonali 'happy' to have helped
OL,4,Cothers with gambling issues during ban
OL,6,F"You have this enormous sort of block
OL,7,Fand this is the biggest step to take
OL,8,Fto resolve this problem."
OL,10,FAlongside his suspension, Tonali has
OL,11,Fundergone an education programme and
OL,12,Falso made 16 trips back to Italy to
OL,13,Fhelp educate the next generation of
OL,14,Fplayers about some of the issues they
OL,15,Fcould encounter.
