OL,3,CSandro Tonali 'happy' to have helped
OL,4,Cothers with gambling issues during ban
OL,6,F"Ten months is a long time, especially
OL,7,Fbecause a footballer lives for
OL,8,F(matchdays), so it was hard work. I
OL,9,Fdid work, though. I trained every day,
OL,10,Feven more than when I was playing."
OL,12,FSpeaking ahead of the game,
OL,13,FNewcastle's head coach Eddie Howe said
OL,14,Fthe midfielder would experience a
OL,15,F"range of emotions on his return."
OL,17,FHe said: "When you have a long time
OL,18,Fout, you have a long time to analyse
OL,19,Fand reflect.
